WEBVTT

00:00:16.349 --> 00:00:19.853
The time has come.
Show your wings...

00:00:20.854 --> 00:00:22.689
Stern Ritters!

00:00:33.491 --> 00:00:37.912
Nobody can take anything
away from me.

00:00:39.831 --> 00:00:44.127
Everything in this world
exists for me to take it.

00:00:44.878 --> 00:00:47.464
The Soul King is no exception.

00:00:47.464 --> 00:00:52.677
{\an8}"SEAL"

00:01:08.818 --> 00:01:11.112
Let's go, my children!

00:01:25.376 --> 00:01:30.924
{\an8}<i>Oh, my darling, I don't even know
where my heart has gone</i>

00:01:31.216 --> 00:01:36.805
{\an8}<i>And I've forgotten
that dream I once had</i>

00:01:36.971 --> 00:01:42.102
{\an8}<i>Becoming an adult =
keeping a public face and bluffing?</i>

00:01:42.769 --> 00:01:48.983
{\an8}<i>Tell me, what is reflected
in the painted-over mirror?</i>

00:01:49.609 --> 00:01:54.781
{\an8}<i>Your photo is starting to fade</i>

00:01:55.323 --> 00:01:59.994
{\an8}<i>Leaving me, as I change</i>

00:01:59.994 --> 00:02:05.834
{\an8}<i>I'll shout at the top of my voice
as it pierces through the night</i>

00:02:06.167 --> 00:02:11.631
{\an8}<i>Burning my chest,
formless fear and all</i>

00:02:11.631 --> 00:02:17.470
{\an8}<i>It's okay if I can't laugh
like that day</i>

00:02:17.595 --> 00:02:23.309
{\an8}<i>Sadness, scars, everything...
I want to take them all with me</i>

00:02:24.310 --> 00:02:26.729
{\an8}<i>You can't kill my vibe, oh baby</i>

00:02:26.729 --> 00:02:29.691
{\an8}<i>Burning out now,
like a shooting star</i>

00:02:30.066 --> 00:02:32.694
{\an8}<i>You can't kill my vibe, oh baby</i>

00:02:32.694 --> 00:02:35.405
{\an8}<i>Burning out now,
like a shooting star</i>

00:02:38.700 --> 00:02:43.746
{\an8}BLEACH: THOUSAND-YEAR BLOOD WAR

00:03:01.764 --> 00:03:03.224
I see...

00:03:03.766 --> 00:03:05.393
So, this must be
the additional power

00:03:05.518 --> 00:03:07.812
shared with you
through the Auswählen...

00:03:08.521 --> 00:03:11.065
That's why your bullet
that couldn't reach me before

00:03:11.191 --> 00:03:14.736
is now able to punch a hole
through my body, yeah...?

00:03:14.986 --> 00:03:16.571
You've got two things wrong.

00:03:17.071 --> 00:03:20.700
The first is that
this is not an additional power.

00:03:21.409 --> 00:03:23.119
It is a power I've always possessed

00:03:23.244 --> 00:03:24.913
that I merely did not have time
to use earlier.

00:03:25.747 --> 00:03:30.627
And the second is that your body
wasn't pierced by a bullet.

00:03:33.630 --> 00:03:35.131
That's why it can't be blocked

00:03:35.256 --> 00:03:36.841
no matter how many walls
you put up.

00:03:41.471 --> 00:03:44.057
The name of my power is "X-Axis."

00:03:44.682 --> 00:03:45.683
There are no bullets.

00:03:45.892 --> 00:03:48.353
It uniformly penetrates
everything in-between

00:03:48.353 --> 00:03:50.355
the muzzle of my gun
and the target.

00:03:52.523 --> 00:03:54.525
Mind lining up in a single file?

00:03:55.068 --> 00:03:56.945
That way I can kill you all
with a single shot.

00:04:02.492 --> 00:04:05.286
Slumbering too soon
has its disadvantages...

00:04:11.084 --> 00:04:14.671
Dead morning!
Everybody, my buddies!

00:04:15.630 --> 00:04:17.632
He's not dead
even after you shot him?

00:04:17.632 --> 00:04:19.050
He's a stubborn one.

00:04:19.884 --> 00:04:22.011
Were you expecting
to make a comeback win

00:04:22.011 --> 00:04:23.554
just because you grew some wings?

00:04:23.554 --> 00:04:25.348
Don't underestimate the five of us.

00:04:25.473 --> 00:04:28.476
We're stronger than the entire
13 Court Guard Squads put together!

00:04:28.685 --> 00:04:30.770
You're living in a dream world

00:04:30.770 --> 00:04:33.815
if you think you can enter
the Royal Palace.

00:04:34.357 --> 00:04:35.817
All right, let's go!

00:05:11.477 --> 00:05:13.354
You're attached to that knife,
aren't you?

00:05:13.688 --> 00:05:15.023
That toy won't work on me.

00:05:15.523 --> 00:05:16.941
What an odd thing to say.

00:05:17.525 --> 00:05:18.693
Shigarami...

00:05:19.027 --> 00:05:20.695
You should watch your words,

00:05:20.820 --> 00:05:22.363
or it will pierce a hole
through your tongue.

00:05:25.408 --> 00:05:29.746
I'm going to be showing you
some real hospitality!

00:05:39.589 --> 00:05:41.090
Heavenly Flash!

00:05:41.257 --> 00:05:42.842
Kinpika!

00:05:43.426 --> 00:05:44.844
Now that's dazzling...

00:06:00.610 --> 00:06:02.278
Hold still, damn it!

00:06:02.278 --> 00:06:03.905
No way!

00:06:04.113 --> 00:06:07.241
You're a fatally bad
matchup for me!

00:06:18.628 --> 00:06:19.962
Good grief...

00:06:19.962 --> 00:06:22.840
You don't seem to realize
how generous I've been.

00:06:23.633 --> 00:06:27.762
Yhw, I went through the trouble
to cut your power in half

00:06:27.762 --> 00:06:30.431
for your own sake...

00:06:31.933 --> 00:06:34.852
After all, you would lose face
to the Quincies

00:06:34.852 --> 00:06:37.605
if I crushed you
while you were at full strength!

00:06:40.066 --> 00:06:43.611
Though reputation isn't
worth a damn once you're dead.

00:06:43.611 --> 00:06:44.987
Hyapporankan!

00:06:45.113 --> 00:06:46.989
Blut Vene Aufheben!

00:06:48.783 --> 00:06:51.953
Secret Hado Number 3: Teppusatsu!

00:06:57.542 --> 00:06:58.543
Gotcha!

00:06:58.668 --> 00:07:00.211
You touched me.

00:07:11.055 --> 00:07:12.432
Unbelievable...

00:07:12.682 --> 00:07:15.476
Not only did you trespass into
the Royal Palace,

00:07:15.476 --> 00:07:18.312
you even trespass into
the body of a Squad Zero member,

00:07:18.438 --> 00:07:19.605
the vassal of the Soul King...

00:07:20.064 --> 00:07:23.025
Enough of your insolence,
you lowly human.

00:07:23.651 --> 00:07:25.361
Time for your punishment.

00:07:26.779 --> 00:07:27.697
Paint it Black...

00:07:30.533 --> 00:07:32.034
Ichimonji.

00:07:37.039 --> 00:07:38.624
What's the matter?

00:07:38.624 --> 00:07:41.627
Can't tell if you're seeing
a brush or a blade?

00:07:51.220 --> 00:07:52.555
What's with that blade?

00:07:52.847 --> 00:07:57.059
It just splashes ink around
and doesn't cut a thing!

00:07:58.436 --> 00:08:02.148
Is it a blade that can cut names
in half like you did earlier?

00:08:02.565 --> 00:08:04.692
But you should already know by now

00:08:04.692 --> 00:08:09.071
that I can restore names and powers
you've cut in half...

00:08:09.071 --> 00:08:11.407
through the use of my own power!

00:08:11.949 --> 00:08:14.285
You cannot defeat me
with that blade.

00:08:14.994 --> 00:08:17.705
I'm going to use my... to...

00:08:18.873 --> 00:08:20.833
Hm?
What was that?

00:08:22.543 --> 00:08:25.254
What's the name of that sword?

00:08:25.630 --> 00:08:26.672
You wouldn't know.

00:08:26.839 --> 00:08:28.758
Or rather, you do know...

00:08:29.133 --> 00:08:32.720
That your sword has no name.

00:08:33.763 --> 00:08:37.517
Anything painted over by Ichimonji
loses its name.

00:08:38.434 --> 00:08:40.728
That without a name has no power.

00:08:41.312 --> 00:08:44.565
And your sword and cross
have no names.

00:08:45.858 --> 00:08:49.195
Did you really think
you could kill me with those?

00:08:54.617 --> 00:08:58.412
You can't kill my heart
with that small needle!

00:09:11.592 --> 00:09:12.593
What?!

00:09:31.737 --> 00:09:32.321
Whoa!

00:09:32.321 --> 00:09:34.740
It's not just our powers
that's a bad matchup for you!

00:09:36.117 --> 00:09:38.661
You're also slower than me!

00:09:47.378 --> 00:09:50.131
I also said this
to the funky guy back there...

00:09:50.464 --> 00:09:52.508
But you shouldn't underestimate me.

00:09:53.593 --> 00:09:55.886
It could be fatal, see?

00:09:58.264 --> 00:09:59.265
<i>What?</i>

00:09:59.724 --> 00:10:00.683
<i>The blade slip right through?</i>

00:10:02.518 --> 00:10:04.562
That's a strange technique
you're using!

00:10:05.187 --> 00:10:07.690
My eyes have gotten
used to your speed.

00:10:08.149 --> 00:10:09.358
The next one will end this.

00:10:10.985 --> 00:10:12.653
Yooo!

00:10:12.862 --> 00:10:14.780
It seems you're quick
to resign yourself.

00:10:20.036 --> 00:10:21.579
You can't shoot, can you?

00:10:22.079 --> 00:10:24.540
Not at Y.H.!

00:10:27.627 --> 00:10:29.378
You took the shot...

00:10:30.004 --> 00:10:34.216
So why is Y.H. unharmed?

00:10:35.509 --> 00:10:36.761
I thought I told you...

00:10:37.219 --> 00:10:41.849
My "X-Axis" uniformly penetrates
everything in-between

00:10:41.849 --> 00:10:44.560
the muzzle of my gun
and the target.

00:10:54.070 --> 00:10:55.363
I see...

00:10:55.738 --> 00:10:58.741
Then I shall steal your power!

00:10:59.575 --> 00:11:03.746
Not with something without a name,
but with my own power!

00:11:05.539 --> 00:11:07.583
Sankt Altar!

00:11:11.545 --> 00:11:15.257
Your "black" has become
my own power...

00:11:29.772 --> 00:11:33.567
You call this being stronger than
the entire 13 Court Guard Squads?

00:11:33.567 --> 00:11:35.194
This is laughable.

00:11:35.736 --> 00:11:37.571
Hasty, aren't we?

00:11:38.406 --> 00:11:42.910
We've yet to use the strength
of even one Court Guard Squad, yo.

00:11:44.495 --> 00:11:47.581
The Royal Special Task Force
that protects the Soul King

00:11:47.581 --> 00:11:50.000
can't let some Quincies
get the better of them!

00:11:50.334 --> 00:11:53.337
Now get up, Squad Zero!
Everybody!

00:11:57.717 --> 00:11:58.718
Senjumaru...

00:11:58.718 --> 00:12:00.886
You'll be the one to kill them.

00:12:01.345 --> 00:12:03.055
Oh?
Are you sure?

00:12:03.639 --> 00:12:07.685
Since you have a thousand arms,
six people should be easy.

00:12:08.060 --> 00:12:09.603
Just don't overdo it.

00:12:09.979 --> 00:12:11.313
That goes without saying.

00:12:13.357 --> 00:12:16.026
We'll show you how Squad Zero
gets serious.

00:12:20.823 --> 00:12:21.782
They killed themselves?!

00:12:37.214 --> 00:12:39.550
You didn't stand a chance against us
when there were four of you.

00:12:39.550 --> 00:12:41.677
What can you do all by yourself?

00:12:42.011 --> 00:12:44.597
Even the slightest use
of our powers would cause

00:12:44.597 --> 00:12:47.183
the heaven and earth
of the three worlds to tremble.

00:12:47.600 --> 00:12:48.934
Because of that,

00:12:49.059 --> 00:12:54.064
we linked our lives to one another
to seal away our true swords.

00:12:55.191 --> 00:12:58.861
And now,
in exchange for three of our lives,

00:12:59.111 --> 00:13:02.490
the blood oath seal
has been broken...

00:13:04.200 --> 00:13:05.367
Prepare yourself.

00:13:07.661 --> 00:13:08.829
Bankai.

00:13:39.693 --> 00:13:42.696
Shatatsu Karagara Shigaraminotsuji.

00:13:51.455 --> 00:13:53.791
<i>Thump... Thump...</i>

00:13:54.625 --> 00:13:56.752
<i>Rattle... Rattle...</i>

00:13:57.753 --> 00:13:58.754
<i>Thump...</i>

00:13:59.088 --> 00:14:00.714
<i>Rattle, rattle...</i>

00:14:04.802 --> 00:14:08.305
<i>Unravel one hank,
Abundant Blooming of Eyes.</i>

00:14:11.600 --> 00:14:15.020
<i>Sightless be to any
who gaze upon their might.</i>

00:14:17.523 --> 00:14:19.108
<i>Unravel two hanks...</i>

00:14:19.233 --> 00:14:20.568
Oh, come on...

00:14:20.568 --> 00:14:22.528
What the heck is this?

00:14:22.987 --> 00:14:24.780
<i>Armor of Blade Steel.</i>

00:14:31.203 --> 00:14:35.583
<i>And you, unable to bear its weight,
are forever sealed.</i>

00:14:37.793 --> 00:14:39.587
<i>Unravel three hanks...</i>

00:14:40.629 --> 00:14:42.715
<i>Bowels of Black Sand.</i>

00:14:45.801 --> 00:14:47.678
<i>Pulled in by those hands...</i>

00:14:51.640 --> 00:14:53.100
<i>you meet your end.</i>

00:14:56.562 --> 00:14:58.480
<i>Unravel four hanks...</i>

00:14:59.607 --> 00:15:01.275
What a petty trick.

00:15:01.650 --> 00:15:02.610
I shall cut right through—

00:15:04.820 --> 00:15:06.780
<i>Freezing Bed Linens.</i>

00:15:09.575 --> 00:15:11.785
<i>Succumb to their slumber...</i>

00:15:12.453 --> 00:15:14.330
<i>and never stir again.</i>

00:15:16.790 --> 00:15:20.336
<i>Unravel five hanks, Burning Field.</i>

00:15:31.597 --> 00:15:33.557
<i>Until you turn to ash...</i>

00:15:35.851 --> 00:15:37.937
<i>there is no escape.</i>

00:15:41.273 --> 00:15:43.192
<i>Unravel six hanks...</i>

00:15:43.567 --> 00:15:45.778
<i>Star of the Dark Night.</i>

00:15:52.326 --> 00:15:54.578
<i>Absorbed by its abyss...</i>

00:16:00.918 --> 00:16:02.711
<i>and led into the afterlife.</i>

00:16:04.755 --> 00:16:07.549
<i>Now take a quick look,
you villains...</i>

00:16:08.676 --> 00:16:13.806
<i>as I bind off and release
the cloths from this loom.</i>

00:16:15.349 --> 00:16:18.644
<i>Shidenorokushikiukimonnohata.</i>

00:16:33.200 --> 00:16:35.494
My power is "Black."

00:16:36.704 --> 00:16:39.707
Once I unleash Ichimonji...

00:16:40.040 --> 00:16:43.711
Soul Reapers, Quincies,
the dead and the living...

00:16:43.711 --> 00:16:45.421
It doesn't matter who you are.

00:16:45.713 --> 00:16:48.424
All the "Black" in this world...

00:16:51.010 --> 00:16:52.970
becomes mine.

00:16:58.767 --> 00:17:00.060
Yhwach.

00:17:00.310 --> 00:17:03.897
Or rather,
the one who used to be Yhwach.

00:17:04.565 --> 00:17:06.734
Losing your name must be agonizing.

00:17:07.568 --> 00:17:09.862
Poor fellow.
How about...

00:17:11.030 --> 00:17:12.906
I give you a name!

00:17:13.574 --> 00:17:17.745
Shinuchi Shirafude Ichimonji.

00:17:18.370 --> 00:17:20.581
If I had to use
the more modern term,

00:17:20.581 --> 00:17:23.208
I guess this would be
called a Bankai.

00:17:23.667 --> 00:17:27.963
After all, this was
the first evolved Zanpakuto

00:17:27.963 --> 00:17:31.800
that was around far before
Bankai existed in the world.

00:17:32.509 --> 00:17:36.096
This sword can etch a new name

00:17:36.096 --> 00:17:39.391
on whatever is painted over
by Ichimonji.

00:17:39.558 --> 00:17:47.566
{\an8}"BLACK ANT"

00:17:41.560 --> 00:17:47.566
Now how do you feel, "Black Ant,"
who was formerly known as Yhwach?

00:17:48.067 --> 00:17:49.943
Your power is like that of

00:17:50.069 --> 00:17:52.738
a black ant
that crawls on the ground—

00:17:52.738 --> 00:17:55.741
a frail and fleeting life.

00:17:57.117 --> 00:17:59.661
I... I never imagined...

00:18:00.662 --> 00:18:02.831
Yes.
You couldn't have imagined.

00:18:03.332 --> 00:18:05.876
The extent of the difference
in our power.

00:18:06.710 --> 00:18:09.838
And this is where your fate ends.

00:18:10.214 --> 00:18:11.590
You will bear the weight of

00:18:11.590 --> 00:18:14.093
the lives of all the Soul Reapers
you’ve killed...

00:18:14.635 --> 00:18:18.514
and be crushed to death
like the black ant that you are!

00:18:22.226 --> 00:18:24.728
King of the bugs...

00:18:26.730 --> 00:18:27.773
Farewell.

00:18:51.755 --> 00:18:56.093
{\an8}<i>All at once, the lights went out</i>

00:18:56.093 --> 00:18:57.386
{\an8}<i>Reminding me</i>

00:18:57.386 --> 00:18:58.637
{\an8}<i>with a voice</i>

00:18:58.637 --> 00:19:00.639
{\an8}<i>and I cannot move</i>

00:19:01.557 --> 00:19:05.811
{\an8}<i>Unable to convey even a millimeter</i>

00:19:05.811 --> 00:19:08.355
{\an8}<i>of the lines that I dubbed</i>

00:19:08.355 --> 00:19:10.649
{\an8}<i>All lines
that I don't want to forget</i>

00:19:10.649 --> 00:19:12.025
{\an8}<i>Rewound</i>

00:19:12.025 --> 00:19:13.152
{\an8}<i>Repeated</i>

00:19:13.152 --> 00:19:14.194
{\an8}<i>Became a mark</i>

00:19:14.319 --> 00:19:15.571
{\an8}<i>And I notice the dust</i>

00:19:15.571 --> 00:19:16.655
{\an8}<i>I wait and wait</i>

00:19:16.655 --> 00:19:18.115
{\an8}<i>But it won't start</i>

00:19:18.240 --> 00:19:19.241
{\an8}<i>If it's already ended</i>

00:19:19.241 --> 00:19:20.617
{\an8}<i>I give up</i>

00:19:20.742 --> 00:19:21.702
{\an8}<i>But can I</i>

00:19:21.702 --> 00:19:22.911
{\an8}<i>borrow your shoulder?</i>

00:19:23.036 --> 00:19:24.580
{\an8}<i>With that knife</i>

00:19:24.580 --> 00:19:26.582
{\an8}<i>that was left behind</i>

00:19:27.583 --> 00:19:29.585
{\an8}<i>Pierce it through</i>

00:19:29.710 --> 00:19:30.878
{\an8}<i>Still</i>

00:19:30.878 --> 00:19:33.213
{\an8}<i>in the middle of a dream,</i>

00:19:33.213 --> 00:19:35.716
{\an8}<i>We kept searching</i>

00:19:35.716 --> 00:19:37.926
{\an8}<i>For the scar that</i>

00:19:37.926 --> 00:19:40.637
{\an8}<i>the revolving world remembers</i>

00:19:40.762 --> 00:19:42.890
{\an8}<i>With just the strong desire</i>

00:19:42.890 --> 00:19:46.268
{\an8}<i>to keep on living</i>

00:19:46.268 --> 00:19:51.440
{\an8}<i>We'll choose a tomorrow
that will not return</i>

00:19:51.440 --> 00:19:56.111
{\an8}<i>In just a little while</i>

00:19:56.236 --> 00:20:00.741
{\an8}<i>The final curtain will fall</i>

00:20:01.366 --> 00:20:04.912
{\an8}<i>Shining upon us</i>

00:20:04.912 --> 00:20:07.915
{\an8}<i>The blurred end roll</i>

00:20:19.176 --> 00:20:20.844
Long time no BLEACH!

00:20:21.094 --> 00:20:22.179
How long has it been?

00:20:22.346 --> 00:20:25.390
To all the ladies!
Oh, and guys too...

00:20:25.807 --> 00:20:26.975
The wait is over!

00:20:27.351 --> 00:20:30.854
It's me, the King of New York,
aka Kon!

00:20:31.521 --> 00:20:34.399
Did you guys enjoy
the Part 2 finale?

00:20:34.399 --> 00:20:37.444
Well, guess what?
Today, we're bringing back

00:20:37.444 --> 00:20:41.406
the mega-popular "Illustrated Guide
to Soul Reapers"!

00:20:41.573 --> 00:20:45.494
I picked out some special footage
of Ichigo and his friends

00:20:45.494 --> 00:20:47.704
doing all sorts of stuff!

00:20:47.704 --> 00:20:49.414
You can thank me later.

00:20:49.706 --> 00:20:52.084
Okay, now let's get started!

00:20:52.626 --> 00:20:55.003
Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!

00:20:55.963 --> 00:20:57.464
<i>"It's Been a While!"</i>

00:20:58.048 --> 00:20:59.549
{\an8}SQUAD 12 BARRACKS

00:20:59.549 --> 00:21:00.634
"Can't fix it"?

00:21:00.634 --> 00:21:04.554
A destroyed Bankai
can <i>never</i> be restored.

00:21:04.846 --> 00:21:07.516
What?!
Then what should I do?

00:21:08.517 --> 00:21:09.518
It's me.

00:21:11.395 --> 00:21:12.437
Huh?

00:21:12.562 --> 00:21:13.397
Come back here!

00:21:13.397 --> 00:21:14.398
Catch him!

00:21:14.398 --> 00:21:17.442
Move, move, move, move, move!

00:21:18.318 --> 00:21:21.238
Oh, crap!
I just punted somebody!

00:21:21.947 --> 00:21:23.156
Wait... Ichigo?

00:21:23.282 --> 00:21:25.450
Hey, you're...
Who are you?

00:21:25.450 --> 00:21:26.535
Who am I?!

00:21:26.535 --> 00:21:29.162
I know it's been a while,
but come on!

00:21:29.329 --> 00:21:31.957
Can't you tell?
It's me!

00:21:32.499 --> 00:21:33.917
Just look at this cute face!

00:21:33.917 --> 00:21:36.003
And this cute face!

00:21:36.003 --> 00:21:37.879
And finally, this cute face!

00:21:38.130 --> 00:21:41.717
I am the King of New York...
aka Kon!

00:21:42.009 --> 00:21:44.761
R-Right...
What can I say...

00:21:45.429 --> 00:21:48.890
I haven't seen you in a while,
but you've grown big?

00:21:48.890 --> 00:21:50.142
Stop!

00:21:50.142 --> 00:21:52.144
Don't sugarcoat it just because

00:21:52.269 --> 00:21:54.604
you feel sorry
for what I've become!

00:21:54.604 --> 00:21:56.315
Hear me out, Ichigo!

00:21:56.315 --> 00:21:58.775
My recent history of suffering...

00:22:01.945 --> 00:22:03.447
So as I was saying...

00:22:03.447 --> 00:22:06.491
Damn it!
He's going back to the main plot!

00:22:06.491 --> 00:22:07.993
He's small now!
Get him!

00:22:10.787 --> 00:22:12.873
Come with me, Ichigo Kurosaki.

00:22:13.123 --> 00:22:15.250
The great Squad Zero is coming.

00:22:18.045 --> 00:22:21.381
<i>"Memories of You-Know-Where."</i>

00:22:21.590 --> 00:22:22.966
{\an8}HYOSUBE'S RIDEN – TRAINING GROUNDS

00:22:23.467 --> 00:22:24.593
Yes, this is Kuchiki!

00:22:25.552 --> 00:22:26.553
Uh-huh...

00:22:26.887 --> 00:22:27.888
Really?!

00:22:28.180 --> 00:22:29.181
Thank you, sir!

00:22:29.598 --> 00:22:30.599
Who is it?

00:22:30.807 --> 00:22:32.184
It was from Sir Kirinji!

00:22:32.559 --> 00:22:34.436
He says my brother has recovered!

00:22:34.436 --> 00:22:35.979
He recovered?!

00:22:36.229 --> 00:22:37.314
Thank goodness...

00:22:37.981 --> 00:22:43.445
Wait, that means he'll eat,
train his sword, and then...

00:22:43.695 --> 00:22:44.738
...go there.

00:22:45.572 --> 00:22:48.033
That place was awful...

00:22:48.158 --> 00:22:49.618
A measurement from hell.

00:22:50.202 --> 00:22:52.287
Yeah...
I was stripped naked.

00:22:52.704 --> 00:22:54.039
I don't even want to
think about it.

00:22:56.666 --> 00:22:59.294
Renji? Hey, why are you
trying to remember it?

00:22:59.461 --> 00:23:02.464
No! Don't do it!
Renji!

00:23:03.632 --> 00:23:05.384
{\an8}SHUTARA'S RIDEN

00:23:05.884 --> 00:23:08.136
<i>– Say what?
– Don't respond with a question.</i>

00:23:08.136 --> 00:23:10.097
<i>You heard me.</i>

00:23:10.514 --> 00:23:12.849
<i>I said take off
your loincloth, too.</i>

00:23:12.974 --> 00:23:13.725
<i>Wait a minute!</i>

00:23:13.850 --> 00:23:15.477
<i>We're taking measurements
for a Shihakusho, right?</i>

00:23:15.477 --> 00:23:18.063
<i>Why can't we do that
with my loincloth on?</i>

00:23:18.063 --> 00:23:21.942
<i>I see... All right.
I understand.</i>

00:23:22.192 --> 00:23:24.611
<i>I'll take measurements
after I remove your jewels.</i>

00:23:24.611 --> 00:23:26.571
<i>Okay!
I'm taking it off right now!</i>

00:23:28.073 --> 00:23:30.409
You back, Renji?!
Thank goodness...

00:23:30.409 --> 00:23:33.328
I'm glad you didn't reach the part
where you took it off!

00:23:34.287 --> 00:23:36.581
But your tragedy aside...

00:23:36.832 --> 00:23:38.667
It pains me to think my brother

00:23:38.667 --> 00:23:41.586
has to go through
the same humiliation...

00:23:41.795 --> 00:23:42.838
My tragedy aside?

00:23:43.296 --> 00:23:45.173
Poor Brother...

00:23:47.300 --> 00:23:49.386
Now that's more like it...

00:23:49.511 --> 00:23:52.514
They need to show
more of this kind of stuff!

00:23:52.514 --> 00:23:54.724
All this tension between
the Soul Reapers and Quincies

00:23:54.850 --> 00:23:57.060
going about their final battle
and separation, yadda, yadda...

00:23:57.060 --> 00:23:58.437
It's way too serious, man!

00:23:58.895 --> 00:24:01.106
So I put my perfect taste
to good use

00:24:01.231 --> 00:24:04.943
by bringing you this special bonus
to go with the Part 2 finale.

00:24:05.152 --> 00:24:06.445
For those of you watching this
in front of the screen,

00:24:06.570 --> 00:24:09.823
show your appreciation with
a round of applause and cheering.

00:24:10.073 --> 00:24:13.160
And that's all for today.

00:24:13.535 --> 00:24:16.955
Stay on the edge of your seats
so you can see me next time!

00:24:17.247 --> 00:24:18.623
Bye!

